Job Details
Candidate will be responsible for selling IPTelephony and Network Solutions to new customers within UAE.
70% of the job role will remain as outdoor activity. Business calls and transportation will be covered
Candidate must be a team player and self-mover.
Previous sales experience of computer, PBX, IPTelephony and Networking  preferred. Fresh candidates with no experience of UAE are also welcomed.
Joining Date: Immediate
